description:
An easy-to-use screen recorder for lessons and tutorials.

Wondershare DemoCreator is a professional presentation video creation tool that integrates recording and editing to help you create videos more efficiently. Using DemoCreator, you can not only experience high-definition screen recording, webcam capture, microphone voice-over recording, screen drawing tool, spotlight, and other practical recording functions. You can also use the built-in video templates, transition effects, green screen chroma key, Pan&Zoom, stickers, and other hundreds of editing tools and presentation video templates to help you create videos with ease.
DemoCreator has made special optimizations for video creation such as presentations, online training, and game recording. It supports the audio and video sub-track editing of the recorded files according to the input source. It uses cursor effects, audio fade-in and fade-out, and other post-production tools to accurately modify the video material so that you can make better use of the video material. During game recording, unique adaptations and optimizations have been made for various popular games to stabilize the image capture and enhance the game recording experience.
New features

1. AI voice cleaner optimization, adjust the clarity and beautification of human voice;

2. Video Presentation mode supports vertical screen recording, users can directly record and generate vertical screen demonstration videos to be released on TK and INS platforms;

3. Video Presentation mode supports camera background blur, effectively focusing on the user subject, enhancing professionalism and immersion

4. Text To Speech function sound color adds P.Star and Morti cartoon sound, suitable for dubbing of children's knowledge videos;

5. Cloud resource pull, realize end-cloud integration

Optimization

1. Added batch application checkbox to subtitle settings;

2. Resource limit free, operation real-time configuration of paid resources as limited free resources according to activities or festivals, improve resource utilization;

3. Support modification of temp folder save path;

4. Split button logic optimization;

5. Support separate export and save thumbnails

6. Added YouTube Shorts (9:16) format

7. Support Ctrl+wheel to zoom in and out of the player

8. Bug optimization-optimize the high-frequency recording problem of user voice
